step_data.thought: I've successfully navigated to the Customer Order Total report page and set the 'From:' date to January 1, 2023. Now I need to set the 'To:' date to ensure I get a complete range of data. Looking at the current page, I can see the 'To:' textbox with ID 754 that needs to be filled. I'll set it to today's date to get all data from January 1, 2023 until now. After setting both date fields, I'll need to click the 'Refresh' button to generate the report that will show high-value customers based on their order totals.
